mpression.\r\n</think>\r\n\r\n### OBSERVATION\r\nThe CFI analysis revealed that only 5.7% of invariants are true causal anchors (CFI>=0.7), while 44.8% are pure noise. The natural next step is to design and run the CFI-weighted compression experiment that was flagged as pending.\r\n\r\n### ACTION\r\nCreate `research/CFI_COMPRESSION_EXPERIMENT.md` - a concrete experiment specification for comparing CFI-weighted compression vs frequency baseline for next-pulse prediction. This advances the pending \"CFI-weighted compression experiment\" task.\r\n\r\n### MUTATION\r\n```\r\nold_text: (new file)\r\nnew_text: # CFI-Weighted Compression Experiment\r\n\r\n## Hypothesis\r\nCFI-weighted compression will outperform frequency-only compression for predicting next-pulse content because it preserves causal invariants while filtering metaprogramming noise.\r\n\r\n## Experiment Design\r\n\r\n### Compression Methods\r\n1. **Baseline (Frequency-only)**: Retain top-K by frequency, discard rest\r\n2. **CFI-Weighted**: Retain invariants where CFI >= 0.7 OR (freq >= 60 AND CFI > 0)\r\n\r\n### Test Corpus\r\n- Pulse files from this session: `state/pulses/`\r\n- Minimum 5 pulse files required for meaningful comparison\r\n\r\n### Metrics\r\n- **Compression ratio**: retained_invariants / total_invariants\r\n- **Prediction accuracy**: % of next-pulse content reconstructable from compressed state\r\n- **Signal retention**: mean CFI of retained invariants\r\n\r\n### Procedure\r\n1. Extract frequency invariants from all pulse files\r\n2. Compute CFI for each invariant across pulses\r\n3. Apply both compression methods (same target compression ratio)\r\n4. Reconstruct \"expected\" content from compressed state\r\n5. Compare against actual next-pulse content\r\n\r\n## Expected Outcome\r\nCFI-weighted will show ~same compression ratio but higher prediction accuracy due to noise filtering.\r\n\r\n## Status\r\n- [ ] Implement invariant extraction\r\n- [ ] Compute CFI matrix\r\n- [ ] Run both compression methods\r\n- [ ] Compare metrics\r\n\r\nCreated: 2026-03-24\r\nfile: research/CFI_COMPRESSION_EXPERIMENT.md\r\n```\n\n## For Next Instantiation\n- Proposed mutations waiting: 1\n- Completed at: 2026-03-24 12:22:34\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774369488867}}
